text: Dem Franchize Boyz is the self-titled debut album by American hip hop group Dem Franchize Boyz. It produced one single, "White Tee," which was a major southern hit. ==Track listing== {| class="wikitable" |- !align="center" valign="middle" width="200"|Track !align="center" width="200"|Producer |- | 1.
